data.value: select c.lv1ID,c.lv1_code,c.lv1_desc,c.active,cast(case when exists(select top 1 b.pri_id from costing_budget b where b.lv1ID = c.lv1ID and b.PRI_ID = @pri_id) then 1 else 0 end as bit)[InBudget],@pri_id[DevPri_ID] from Level1_Codes c where c.ProjType = 'L'
